I am trying to say here!

356
00:31:26,986 --> 00:31:28,928
Okay, if you put me
in the game,

357
00:31:29,322 --> 00:31:32,421
Brad Bramish is gonna do
what needs to be done, baby.

358
00:31:32,490 --> 00:31:34,432
Okay?
But they don't put me in!

359
00:31:34,570 --> 00:31:37,385
What needs doing,
ain't gonna get done!

360
00:31:37,450 --> 00:31:40,003
Huh? And then
don't come crying to me.

361
00:31:40,201 --> 00:31:43,714
Boo-hoo-hoo-hoo! If you don't
put me in the game!

362
00:31:44,202 --> 00:31:46,984
Now, am I right?
Of course I'm right!

363
00:31:47,338 --> 00:31:49,793
