Just listening.

367
00:32:04,874 --> 00:32:07,721
All right, you got me.
I'm a scout for the Gophers.

368
00:32:07,785 --> 00:32:11,233
Been watching your game
for a month, but that story
right there, just clenched it.

369
00:32:11,306 --> 00:32:14,306
