go somewhere more private.

379
00:32:36,329 --> 00:32:39,231
With you? Sure.

380
00:32:48,074 --> 00:32:51,270
If this boy knows what's good
for him, he'll just beat it.

381
00:32:52,682 --> 00:32:55,049
